textAfterTable: 52872 Okyrhoe           Discovered 1998 Sept. 19 by Spacewatch at Kitt Peak. Okyrhoe was the daughter of Chiron and Chariklo. The name means "swift running" or "fast flowing". A prophet, she was changed into a mare by the gods as punishment for revealing their plans to humankind.
